    "It is important to stress here that the structure of a Convolutional Neural Network mostly requires gridded input data.",
    "Thus, the extension toward irregular polygonal partitions such as the ones mentioned above would also require an adaptation of our ENN toward graph-based architectures (Scarselli et al., 2008).",
